Author: yamasukas
Text: I work at a resturaunt so we get half off on most food, and it has really good hamburgers with whatever toppings you want for like $6. I usually put jalapenos and mushrooms on it, I'd send you one if I could!

Author: ahegaoba
Text: Don't beat yourself up about it, the brain doesn't think clearly when it's preoccupied with food. I've gotten in many fights with my bf because of my ED, and I'm sure a lot of people on this sub have. Now I kinda want a burger though... What kind was it?
